CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1946, pg. 4, reads: "GREETINGS - These youngsters, Barbara Ficklin and Lawrence Bagwell, have caught the real spirit of St. Valentines' Day and lost no time in making it a happy occasion. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Copy of a photograph of Lawrence Bagwell kissing Barbara Ficklin on cheek, Ficklin holding Valentine card inscribed "Dad," in domestic interior
